ApproxsimClient.TaclanV2
Class ParsedIdentifier

java.lang.Object
  ApproxsimClient.TaclanV2.ParsedObject
      ApproxsimClient.TaclanV2.ParsedIdentifier

public class ParsedIdentifier
extends ParsedObject

An object representing an identifier of the Taclan language. As such it contains artefacts of the language, it also contains the non lexical type checks.
